          <title>WNBA expansion team Portland Fire reveals new jerseys</title>
          <description><![CDATA[WNBA expansion team the Portland Fire has unveiled its inaugural game jerseys. The white home jersey has Fire emblazoned on the front, and the away red jersey showcases the city&#8217;s name. The secondary logo is PDX, shorthand for the city, with the P as an outline of Mt.]]></description>
